\if{html}{\out{</div>}}
}
\subsection{Details}{
This is computed from \code{sigmaPosterior/sigmaPrior} at the root node,
which equals the sum over all trees of \code{prior(T) * p(data | T)},
normalised by the prior partition function.
}

}
